\tab
\begin{large}
\textbf{6.1 Results}\\
\end{large}

\tab The implementation of the Dirt Defender Ceiling Fan system has yielded significant and positive results, as shown in figure 6.1 in simplifying fan upkeep:\\
\begin{itemize}
    \item The specialized sensors autonomously detect dust accumulation on fan blades, ensuring timely cleaning interventions and maintaining optimal fan performance.
    \item Through a dedicated mobile app, users have gained control over the cleaning process with a simple tap, enhancing convenience and user experience, as illustrated in figure 6.2.
    \item The system's mechanical components, such as small brushes or rubber wipers, effectively remove dust from fan blades without causing damage, ensuring efficient cleaning and prolonging fan lifespan.
    \item The system's integrated dust collection mechanism efficiently stores removed dust in a designated container, eliminating the need for manual cleaning and reducing maintenance efforts.
\end{itemize}

